</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_49" id="24v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft zu
                            <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g,</expan> vicztum in Nider Payern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als uns ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie ir mit
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> sune <expan>Heymra<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        Nothaft, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> zum Barkstein, als von der sache
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> des <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        zu der Weyden also gerett habt, <add><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wir
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ratschr<ex>eiber</ex></expan> bey <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> gehabt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>jecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> ze
                            <expan>Strawbing<ex>en</ex></expan></add>, daz
                                    <add><expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> ewr sune</add> der sache
                        bey ewch <expan>belibe<ex>n</ex></expan> sey und ir hoft ein
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> end und
                            <expan>aynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> sein und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ze treff<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiszkl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> daz ir ewch in den
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gemüet und so
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beweiset habt, und lassen ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir der sache auch also bey
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <add>Auch tun wir</add> ewch ze
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns etlich
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawffleüt fürbracht
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie den der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ewr sune etlich hab und
                                <expan>kawffmansch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<add>zu der Weyden</add> aufgehalten hab <pb facs="#facs_50" id="25r"/>und mayne, daz
                                <expan>dass<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<add>gut</add> niht recht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>zollt</expan> sulle sein. Da
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>maine<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>, der
                        wagen, der ir gut gefürt hab, sey recht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>zollt</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, also <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, ir wellet
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>̈m</expan> sune durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> also <expan>verschr<ex>eiben,</ex></expan>
                        daz er sich gen den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> darinn beweise, daz icht ein
                                <expan>unschuldig<ex>er</ex></expan> eins
                            <expan>schuldig<ex>en</ex></expan> engelte, und, ob sich ein
                                <expan>furma<ex>n</ex></expan> iht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gessen</expan>
                        hett, daz er dennoch den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> guten
                                <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweise. Und tut in den
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als wir ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol getrawn. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
